{"tid":1327897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲大家如果受黑犬無理對待，事後要立即用紙同筆記住情況！","createTime":"2019-07-17T18:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T18:34:44.000Z","uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5308a56daaa3cf038b9242f3d570f440c3b4b77b","tid":1327897,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:25:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">然後收埋去安全地方。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然未必會係短期內會有用，但正所謂「今日唔知聽日事」，「一朝天子一朝神」。<br />\n<br />\n他朝一日無論立法會用權力及特權條例又好，獨立調查委員會又好，追究所有違法警察時，都有機會需要你地嘅證供。當你被傳召時，你作為第一身證人或受害者就需要依d記憶！<br />\n<br />\n有埋錄音或錄影就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信我記憶會模糊，文字有助還原記憶。<br />\n<br />\n最後警告各位警察，切勿以身試法。<br />\n你知啦，七警當年都估唔到被人篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出更時實有小隊record，實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5d3430d10ce702792b8a26ba7f4d3ebffcc23a","tid":1327897,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"「721文宣」  再次呼籲警員 及指引<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327838</a>"},{"pid":"e37b402d77bff7fd28b2f9235ff43f774d08a843","tid":1327897,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e27fd7ebdaffedeb3eaf4e7711c0640e067710","tid":1327897,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}